Starter template for bitcoin crowd funding website.

To see an example: 
http://eugenelin89-bitstarter-mooc.herokuapp.com/

The template utilizes Twitter Bootstrap Framework v2.3.2 (http://getbootstrap.com/2.3.2/) to implement responsive design (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Responsive_web_design).

The template is intended to be extended using Server Side Java Script with Node.js (http://nodejs.org/)

The template uses the service of Coinbase (https://coinbase.com/) for collecting bitcoins 

SETUP

1. Install Node.js
2. Clone this project in your local file system.
3. Install express by running the following command in the directory where this project is cloned:
npm install express
4. Start the project by running:
node web.js

By default, the server litens to port 8080.




